---
const highlights = [
  'Frontend Development',
  'Developer Relations',
  'Public Speaking',
  'Community Building',
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-8 px-6 md:pt-10 md:pb-20 bg-muted/30">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-6 md:space-y-10">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium text-foreground sm:text-4xl">About Me</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:space-y-5 sm:text-base md:space-y-6 md:text-lg">
      <p>
        I bring together frontend engineering, DevRel, and community work to create experiences people can actually use, learn from, and feel welcomed by.
      </p>
      <p>
        Through PinkTech and freeCodeCamp events, I turn ideas into workshops, talks, and spaces where developers can grow together.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      {
        highlights.map((highlight) => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs sm:px-4 sm:py-2 sm:text-sm md:px-5 md:py-2.5 md:text-base bg-card/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border rounded-lg text-foreground shadow-sm hover:bg-card transition-all dark:bg-[var(--pink-soft)] dark:border-primary/25 dark:hover:bg-[var(--pink-medium)]">
            {highlight}
          </span>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
